 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Real Estate Buyer's Agent The Margolis Team Inc Brighton, CO 80601 Job details Salary $60,000 - $120,000 a year Job Type Full-time Full Job Description The Margolis Team Inc  of KW Preferred Realty (Top 20 Colorado Award Winning Team!) 
Guarantee your success by working with The Margolis Team Inc. Focus on an opportunity that offers training, leads, coaching, systems, and fun. 
Brand New or Experienced Agents! 
TRAINING
 We offer world-class training! We have a dedicated Team Leader, Brian Margolis who works with you on one plus our team lead is a Real Estate Coach for one of the top Coaching companies in the country. When you work with The Margolis Team, you receive 1 on 1 training plus access to the coaching company at no charge. Don't get lost in a crowd with an office of 25, 50, or 100+ agents. Work on a small team that cares about you, your goals, and your dreams. 
LEADS... Leads... Leads... 
On your first day, you will have access to a lead bank of over 3,000 leads. This isn't a phone book thrown on your desk as many companies will offer you, but 1,000 leads that have made an inquiry on a house to purchase at some time. Plus we receive 100 to 200 new opportunities every month! 
SYSTEMS SYSTEMS SYSTEMS
 Leads and training will only get you so far. Without systems on how to properly manage the leads, an agent's chances for success will quickly dwindle. From a CRM that is the best in the business to Automation and Artificial Intelligence. The Margolis Team is a team that utilizes technology to help you work less and make more money. 
Realistically earn up to $60,000+ in the first 12 months if you are open to learning and training and following our proven systems! 
