Compensation: 
$60,000 - $120,000+ Commission 
Responsibilities: 
Meet with clients in order to discover what they are looking for in their dream home; then find properties that meet their needs 
Consistently network and market to prospect for new customers 
Participate in  open houses , networking activities to enhance your sales 
Present purchase offers to sellers and gets buyers Under Agreement - We will handle all administrative work 
Attend Zoom and or in-person team meetings 
Consistently network and market to prospect for new customers 
Guide 15 to 40 buyer clients through the home purchase process each year 
"Always be consulting" by providing your clients with your very best service and your very best advice 
Qualifications: 
Be a  team player : helping others and willing to learn. 
Current Real Estate License or willingness to get one  (We can help with this-we do not pay for your license- you need skin in the game to succeed). 
Display a people-oriented,  positive,  and customer-focused attitude 
Understand computer-internet basics 
Display excellent verbal and written communication skills 
Exercise active listening and active questioning skills to build rapport and uncover client needs 
Show good organizational and time management skills. 
 
About Company 
 
